Read AGENTS.md for the full project guide.

Key rules:
- Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript strict, Tailwind CSS v4
- @/ path alias for imports
- Components are named exports, pages are default exports
- No em dashes in writing. Use commas or periods.
- Editorial voice: direct, personal, concise. Not corporate.
- Dark-only theme, 640px max width, minimalist design
- Color tokens in app/globals.css under @theme inline
- Detailed context in docs/project-context.md
